Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:10.99,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:38.55,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Controlling blood. That is my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:41.88,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I cast that spell on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:45.98,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I've been able to manipulate \Nyour blood as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:47.94,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Now, for your first task...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:52.78,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I shall force you to kill everyone \Nhere with your own two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:56.28,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Kill every last one of them perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:01:00.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta fell under the Queen of Witches' \Ncontrol and tried to kill his friends, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:04.41,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Make him stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:05.25,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:08.63,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot escape me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:13.13,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you are my daughter. My family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:15.13,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... part of your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:19.51,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:23.06,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:28.82,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A new spell activated, arising from \NVanessa's strong love for her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:36.40,main,queen,0000,0000,0000,,The red thread... of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.91,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Puppet's Blood has come undone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:49.42,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This magic only takes the side of myself \Nand those I have a family bond with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:53.80,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You and I have no bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:20.03,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(187,1)}I'm Home
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:30.10,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You and I have no bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.32,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:39.32,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, look! \NI made a doll out of thread!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.95,flashback,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,My, it's so well-made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:48.85,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make everyone smile with my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.71,flashback,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be able to, Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:02.25,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I obsessed so much over obtaining perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:05.33,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,that I forgot something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:13.23,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,There is a power you can obtain from \Nyour feelings {\i0}because{\i1} you're imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:17.10,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,The magic you could not\Nobtain under my care...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:20.15,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,It came to you only because \Nyou were free and imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.53,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:28.28,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:31.54,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,You have utterly defeated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:38.26,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Recovery Magic:\NCurse-Breaking Blood-Filled Cocoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:16.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.18,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds have healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.05,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:30.55,italics,Final,0000,0000,0000,,She fully healed all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:33.56,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen of Witches really is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:46.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We... won?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:56.95,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:01.67,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We won... We won because of your magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:06.55,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.10,main,Fanzel,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.93,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.44,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how worried I was about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.93,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:18.89,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're naked, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.60,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:24.25,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.98,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:33.49,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.12,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.63,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:47.13,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's because all of you were there for \Nme that I was able to use that spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.26,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:55.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:57.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo! It doesn't hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:04.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt at all! Actually, \NI feel as light as a feather!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.83,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The moment he gets back on his feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:07.89,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:11.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Stupidsta! You're practically naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're bringing that up now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:15.10,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he took after you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.08,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But just look at me now, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:21.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I was healed, I felt like \Nmy muscles were even more powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Stupidsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:35.21,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,This bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:42.10,main,Witch 1,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness those violent \Npeople finally left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.23,main,Witch 2,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they get for \Nattacking the Witches' Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:50.73,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:54.13,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,was apparently looking for a \Nmagic stone that's in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.87,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:08:00.48,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I would assume the magic \Nstone you speak of is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:04.33,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need of it. You may have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The magic stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:10.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:14.15,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap! We got the \Nmagic stone just that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:16.14,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yami's gonna praise us for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:20.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it seemed like the Eye of \Nthe Midnight Sun wanted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:22.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, who the heck are they, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:32.82,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,That magic stone is a magical item \Nthat heightens the wearer's powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:36.49,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,but only those of the elf tribe\N are truly able to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Elves?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.41,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,The elves possessed great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:48.09,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,They lived in what is now called the \NForsaken Realm several centuries ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:51.97,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Each individual elf had an extraordinary \Namount of magical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:55.88,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Many of them were equal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:59.97,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Several centuries? Lady, how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.64,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Your skin is way too flawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.03,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:08.98,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,The humans outnumbered them, and when \Nthey fought them, the elves were annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:13.40,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,That Fana girl's third eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.74,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,That is forbidden magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:22.37,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,But that girl wasn't the one who \Nactivated that spell. It was someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:26.50,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinary humans are unable to \Nmeddle with forbidden magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so completely lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.05,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Activating a forbidden spell
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:36.03,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,requires a tremendous amount of \Nmana and some sort of sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:40.07,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,The ancient demon was also \Na top-level forbidden spell
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:42.81,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,activated by the leader of the elf clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:55.57,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,It could be that the Eye of the Midnight Sun\Nare descendants of the elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:02.68,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me the evil \Nmonsters from the picture book
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,my nanny read to me as a\N child were actually elves?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:08.69,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap! We're getting a \Nton of amazing new intel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:12.55,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting! I'm gonna \Nbecome a reporting fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:16.79,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,And Asta, the two swords you bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:21.69,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,They are the ruined remains of the \Nmagic swords used by the elves' leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:26.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:30.40,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's head exploded because he couldn't \Nkeep up with the conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.48,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Stupidsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:35.28,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He can't! He's too dumb to \Nhandle any more of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:40.95,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue to fight them, that mystery \Nshould also be resolved eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.91,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:50.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you're really going back \Nto the Diamond Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.29,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:57.53,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen of Witches sealed the effects \Nof Puppet's Blood into this medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:01.58,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass it off as some longevity \Ndrug and give it to the king,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.80,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,and put an end to Morris's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:08.81,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll remake the Diamond Kingdom\N into a peaceful nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:12.66,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that I'll help Mars out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:18.49,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,That seems like the quickest way to get into \Nthe top ranks of the Diamond Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.20,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, can we trust this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:24.78,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become someone you can approve of,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:28.58,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,and one day I'll come to \Nvisit you again, Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:31.67,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep Fana with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.50,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Mars, Ladros, don't push yourselves too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:37.14,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We'll take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:40.51,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to make sure she doesn't \Nhave to see Master naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:45.26,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana, I'm sorry. Please wait\N until I've changed the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:49.37,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that I'll make the Diamond Kingdom \Nthe sort of place you can return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:54.94,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait as long as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:12:00.21,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Once the Diamond Kingdom is peaceful, \Nlet's go see the world together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:01.53,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:05.49,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:08.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, one day, that'll be you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.41,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.81,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You called me a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:18.13,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,If you run into trouble, I'll come help \Nyou at any time, no matter where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:21.97,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,That's what friends are for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever need any help, let me know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:28.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blast my way right \Ninto the Diamond Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.69,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,You are free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:42.49,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,But this is still your birthplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.45,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,You may come to visit whenever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:13:00.10,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,If I start at number two,\NI'll be at the top in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:03.51,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't forget to support Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:05.77,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.80,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.39,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:13.86,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished your goodbyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:17.19,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get the heck out of this creepy forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:22.93,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man... I didn't have a chance \Nto get close to any of the witchies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.57,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:29.63,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for healing Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:31.59,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,See you again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:39.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami! My arms are fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.84,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We actually made it back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.84,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to everyone, I'm healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:46.52,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:47.63,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you half-naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:54.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami! We found a magic stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:55.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:58.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, kid. Here's your first mission \Nsince getting your arms fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.28,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Go get me some booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'll go at maximum speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:08.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, the others aren't back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:11.24,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? They probably dropped \Ndead in a ditch somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:17.37,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. If you don't want \Nto die too, get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:24.25,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yo. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.08,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:41.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I bought you some!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.59,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That really was fast. Talk about creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So what's my next mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:49.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:52.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're working too much. \NNo more missions for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:55.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Also, put some damn clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:55.91,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:15:01.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No way... If you take my missions \Naway from me, what do I have left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:02.88,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:06.01,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. You don't need to cry that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:09.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I brought you some clothes. \NHurry up and put them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.26,main,Manga,0000,0000,0000,,We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're finally back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:15.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's Magna's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:21.37,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Magna and Luck went to \Na dungeon to find a way to fix my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:23.02,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta thank them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:31.66,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! \NSomething crazy happened to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:36.77,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Fallen angel who lost your wings... \NIn order to see you smile again,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:38.25,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,we traveled to a dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.98,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We were lost in the dark, drowning in despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:43.65,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,and my heart came close \Nto breaking many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:46.88,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,But every time that happened, \NI would see a vision of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:51.40,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You shook my soul. I killed my \Nweaker self and continued fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.62,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Did his personality completely change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.50,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The mana is calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:58.18,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:03.40,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We wandered the dungeon, disposed of \Nour enemies, and I became more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.65,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,But there was just one important \Nthing I couldn't find:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.90,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,a spell to heal the wounds \Nthat torment you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.76,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Powerless and defeated, I had to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:15.13,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The mana is calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:18.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my arms are fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:24.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Well, \Ngood for you, you little punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.17,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Asta! Now let's kill each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:30.38,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.66,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:37.95,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Gauche and Gordon also went \Nto the royal library to fix my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.35,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta thank them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:44.48,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! They turned into nerds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:48.00,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I have awakened to the splendor of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:50.65,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful spell arrays are like paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.00,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Master Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.61,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, why did your \Npersonality change, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:17:01.29,sign_24357_235_Magic_truly_is_t,Sign/Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Magic truly is the ultimate artistic masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:01.29,italicstop,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I still have no idea what you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:04.82,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But, but, we still haven't found a \Ncure for your arms, Master Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:07.84,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long it takes,\Nwe'll find a way to remove the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.67,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, please wait, \Nplease wait, I implore you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:13.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my arms are fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:19.68,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, you little punk?! \NI said I'd fix them someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:22.15,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Go get yourself cursed again, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:23.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:26.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your nose is bleeding, Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:30.25,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It's from rage, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.69,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:34.80,sign_25255_248_I_know___,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:37.80,sign_25255_248_I_know___,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,That your nose only bleeds
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:41.05,sign_25365_250_when_you_wish_re,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,when you wish really hard for someone\N important to you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:45.43,sign_25365_250_when_you_wish_re,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that because this was the first time\N we'd ever been alone together for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:50.69,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This might be the way to cure Asta's arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.75,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, that won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:56.24,sign_25365_250_when_you_wish_re,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,It always happens when you\N think about your little sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.95,sign_25365_250_when_you_wish_re,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,but your nose was secretly bleeding when\N you were thinking about Asta, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:06.23,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This is dumb. I'm going \Nto stare at Marie now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:08.96,sign_25255_248_I_know___,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,You actually care about Asta
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.71,sign_25365_250_when_you_wish_re,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,just as much as you care for your little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:15.51,sign_24357_235_Magic_truly_is_t,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,Just like your sister, yes, Asta is family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:19.30,sign_24357_235_Magic_truly_is_t,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that since I'm Asta's\Nbest friend, I'm also your family...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.47,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Charmy—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.42,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.42,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, it's me, Charmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.96,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I got infested with magic mushroom parasites.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.88,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Should you really be eating those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:42.43,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I can't transform properly! \NThis is so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.76,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Should you really be embarrassed right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:48.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Charmy! Don't eat any more of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:50.57,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:53.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You ate one, and three more sprouted up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.45,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Here, try one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:01.76,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I picked lots of other yummy things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:04.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You risked your lives for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:08.90,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sorry... We couldn't \Nfind a way to fix your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:12.09,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:16.54,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,You're cured! How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:18.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's really nothing \Nembarrassing about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:23.67,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks like we've got \Nplenty of food and drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:28.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making muscle-for-brains \Nover there take a break,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:30.81,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,so let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:33.73,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Party time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:39.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice to be able to eat with my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:44.48,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, since no one was around this morning, \NI didn't get to feed them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:46.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:52.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You guys must be starving. \NDon't worry, I've got plenty for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:59.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course this happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:02.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. No one's done the laundry, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:05.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I supposed to hang all these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:08.22,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,No one's cleaned the place, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:14.76,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:15.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:22.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of toilet paper. Go get me some.\N And who told you to open the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:25.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And on to the next!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:34.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The captain told him to rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:37.17,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,but he's not getting a chance to rest at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:41.42,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure that's fine for Stupidsta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:49.18,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... This is where I feel most at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,To to mention—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:58.57,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:02.28,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The thing I found in the outside world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.85,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,is my other family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:42.34,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:41.64,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:45.84,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}I Wonder Why
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:44.81,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I Wonder Why.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:22:48.84,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:54.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Fana doesn't get burned \Nwhen Salamander is covered in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:22:55.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Probably because it's magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:23:00.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why your clothes don't get \Nwet inside the Sea Dragon's Lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.63,0:23:02.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:06.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't konbu seaweed \Nflavor the ocean like dashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.34,0:23:09.72,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Leave any food questions \Nto me, Professor Charmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:14.87,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,The component that gives konbu dashi its \Nflavor, glutamic acid, lies within its cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:17.55,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Those cells have what's called \N"selective permeability,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:19.87,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,which gives it the ability \Nto take in what's necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.87,0:23:21.62,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,and get rid of everything it doesn't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:25.41,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,The glutamic acid that creates the dashi \Nin konbu is necessary for its survival,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:28.66,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,so it doesn't leave its cells while \Nit's still alive within the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:31.52,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,But once it dies and is dried, \Nthe cells break apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.52,0:23:33.89,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,causing the glutamic acid to come out,\N which turns into dashi.
